  "2252680": {
    "name": "星球田园诗",
    "steam_appid": 2252680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/dc37372c707fc5e016b573f13aeabff0.avif?t=1772089406\" width=720 height=302 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正在寻求改变生活方式的你，看到了无法抗拒的诱惑：一整颗星球在售，价格极其优惠！这是位于某一太阳系外围的古老农业岩石行星，已经废弃多年。就这样，仅凭一艘破旧的飞船和私人机器助理，你决定在那个星系里被遗忘的角落开启人生新篇章。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/763ef15957afc0866326d0f783113818.poster.avif?t=1772089406\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/763ef15957afc0866326d0f783113818.webm?t=1772089406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/763ef15957afc0866326d0f783113818.mp4?t=1772089406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/8380276f64192f50cb5fc0ed1d06e02e.avif?t=1772089406\" width=600 height=186 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让你的星球重焕生机！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除草、开路、垦荒，并修复随着时间流逝而损坏的事物。将古老的农业岩石星球变为生机勃勃的田园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/247d1799c9f2c2f6a251313d723ea7a7.poster.avif?t=1772089406\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/247d1799c9f2c2f6a251313d723ea7a7.webm?t=1772089406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/247d1799c9f2c2f6a251313d723ea7a7.mp4?t=1772089406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/46270a5a5f7d4b3638048ee145f0ca57.avif?t=1772089406\" width=600 height=186 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索这个太阳系！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管你的飞船状况已经不复当年，但仍然能够帮你在这个太阳系的行星间移动，探索不同星球，收集资源改善农场状况，升级工具与飞船。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/97f99e82f9f5a5ecf15225dc4ffbf48a.poster.avif?t=1772089406\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/97f99e82f9f5a5ecf15225dc4ffbf48a.webm?t=1772089406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/97f99e82f9f5a5ecf15225dc4ffbf48a.mp4?t=1772089406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/848f9014110871400097167b48522e04.avif?t=1772089406\" width=600 height=186 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为社区的一员！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与仍然居住在这个太阳系各个行星上的一小撮居民建立关系。了解他们的故事和决意留守这个星系偏僻角落的原因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/c211bbf41a45d71484c6ec75338f7063.poster.avif?t=1772089406\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/c211bbf41a45d71484c6ec75338f7063.webm?t=1772089406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/c211bbf41a45d71484c6ec75338f7063.mp4?t=1772089406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252680/extras/698362bd29353c56042d8d5d8cd6deb1.avif?t=1772089406\" width=600 height=186 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>拯救这个太阳系，恢复往日的荣光！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一整颗行星，价格却如此优惠？可能这背后有隐情……也许一切并没有看上去那么简单！</p>",
